        "subject": "LU-414 initialized the unused area in MDT's CATALOGS",
        "message": "LU-414 initialized the unused area in MDT's CATALOGS\n\nduring connecting OSTs in MDT, it will call mds_lov_update_desc/obd_llog_init\nto initialize the llog for this OST, and if an OST with big index is connected\nbefore these with small index, an area in MDT's CATALOGS file will be left to\nbe uninitialized, which will cause various problems.\n\nChange-Id: I157ed9792892d4824c7f6d19139577f3e939ed15\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
